						               													<description>Word Turners is a fun alphabet playing card game for 2-6 players, with the simple aim 'who can make the longest word?'It is a game for the whole family and has no time consuming set up, just shuffle and play. There are 60 cards in pack 1 instruction card, 2x 26 alphabet cards and introducing the choice card for which there are 7!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Simply shuffle the cards and deal 7 cards per player, then everyone looks at their cards and decides how many if any to swap, you only get one chance to swap so choose wisely! The choice cards can be any letter you choose! Then when everyone is ready they turn their cards to reveal their word. If there is a draw symbols on  cards come in play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the longest word wins the hand. In the event of a tie, the person with the highest scoring word wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
